		<title>UI Health Craniofacial Center to celebrate holidays with patients, families</title>
		<link>https://today.uic.edu/ui-health-craniofacial-center-to-celebrate-holidays-with-patients-families-2</link>
		<pubDate>Thu, 06 Dec 2018 15:00:05 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Jacqueline Carey]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Health Sciences Colleges]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Patient Care]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[UI Hospital]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Craniofacial Center]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[holiday events]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[UI Health]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://today.uic.edu/?p=71704</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[Center partners with Face the Future Foundation to host event]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<div class="pf-content"><p>The UI Health Craniofacial Center will host a holiday party for young patients, infant to 15 years old. Pediatric patients born with cleft lip and palate or other craniofacial birth conditions, their families and center staff — more than 500 people in all — will celebrate with Santa, holiday crafts, food, gifts, music and surprises.</p>
<h2><a href="https://today.uic.edu/ui-health-craniofacial-center-to-celebrate-holidays-with-patients-families/christmas-cookies-2918172_1920"><img class="alignright wp-image-61763 size-medium" src="https://today.uic.edu/files/2017/12/christmas-cookies-2918172_1920-387x258.jpg" alt="decorated cookies in a bowl" width="387" height="258" srcset="https://today.uic.edu/files/2017/12/christmas-cookies-2918172_1920-387x258.jpg 387w, https://today.uic.edu/files/2017/12/christmas-cookies-2918172_1920-768x512.jpg 768w, https://today.uic.edu/files/2017/12/christmas-cookies-2918172_1920-590x393.jpg 590w, https://today.uic.edu/files/2017/12/christmas-cookies-2918172_1920-1000x667.jpg 1000w, https://today.uic.edu/files/2017/12/christmas-cookies-2918172_1920-500x333.jpg 500w, https://today.uic.edu/files/2017/12/christmas-cookies-2918172_1920-300x200.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 387px) 100vw, 387px" /></a>WHEN:</h2>
<p>Dec. 8<br />
