<h2>DETAILS:</h2>
<p>The party is sponsored by the Face the Future Foundation and Star Events.</p>
<p>The UI Health Craniofacial Center is one of the oldest and largest facilities in the world dedicated to the evaluation and treatment of infants, children, adolescents and adults with cleft lip and palate and other craniofacial conditions. A team approach is the hallmark of the center, where medical specialists and health professionals join together to provide interdisciplinary, comprehensive care in a single location. The center calls on all the resources of UIC&#8217;s academic medical center within the comfort of a private, child-friendly environment where patients are evaluated and treated.</p>
<p>The foundation&#8217;s volunteers raise money to support patient care services and programs at UI Health&#8217;s Craniofacial Center, and to help provide care for patients whose insurance may not cover the full range of needed services. Members of the Face the Future Foundation, Star Events staff and Craniofacial Center staff donate their time and funds to hold this annual event.</p>
